   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Connecting Detroit Youth to a Brighter Future</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Despite the challenges in Detroit we have been able to reduce youth substance use.  90% of the students The Youth Connection serves graduate from high school and either go on to college, pursue a career, or enlist to serve our country. We expose youth to new opportunities to grow, learn and serve their communities that encourage them to see beyond their neighborhoods. We encourage, engage, and support families and our results speak to our passion for helping youth connect to a brighter future.</narrative>
  </description>
